---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import LandingNav from '../components/landing/LandingNav.astro';
import LandingFooter from '../components/landing/LandingFooter.astro';
---
<BaseLayout title="About - ConstructWise">
  <div class="min-h-screen bg-white pt-16">
    <LandingNav />

    <!-- Hero Section -->
    <section class="py-20 bg-gradient-to-br from-blue-50 to-white">
      <div class="container mx-auto px-4 text-center">
        <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold mb-6 bg-clip-text text-transparent bg-gradient-to-r from-blue-600 to-indigo-600">
          The Construction Platform to Plan Smarter
        </h1>
        <p class="text-xl text-gray-600 max-w-3xl mx-auto mb-8">
          At ConstructWise we're committed to building software for construction professionals. Estimators and schedulers spend dozens of hours a week analyzing files, building Excel models, and entering data one activity at a time &mdash; valuable yet manual and time-consuming work that limits your company's project win rates and profitability.
        </p>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="py-20 text-center bg-gray-50">
      <div class="mx-auto px-4">
        <div class="order-2 md:order-1">
          <h2 class="text-3xl font-semibold mb-8">Purpose built for the Construction Industry</h2>
          <div class="container mx-auto px-4">
            <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-6">
              <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-xl shadow-md border border-gray-100">
                <div class="text-xl font-semibold my-2">General Contractors</div>
                <p class="text-gray-600">Automatically generate multi-trade, comprehensive bids and then customize to your risk tolerance. Easily retrieve all the information that's living in file folders, document clouds, and emails so you submit proposals with confidence.</p>
              </div>
              <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-xl shadow-md border border-gray-100">
                <div class="text-xl font-semibold my-2">Developers</div>
                <p class="text-gray-600">When you're developing conceptual budgets for a new development, or you're in the thick of construction, ConstructWise will help you manage your cost basis, track draws with confidence, and deliver projects the way you underwrote them.</p>
              </div>
              <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-xl shadow-md border border-gray-100">
                <div class="text-xl font-semibold my-2">Trade Contractors</div>
                <p class="text-gray-600">If you generate repetitive bid estimates or have a detailed menu of items, use ConstructWise to review for accuracy, pesky Excel errors, or benchmarking against your own data.</p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="py-20 bg-gradient-to-br from-blue-50 to-white">
      <div class="container mx-auto px-4 text-center">
        <p class="text-3xl font-semibold text-gray-600 max-w-3xl mx-auto mb-8">
          We help make sense of all the unstructured numeric data in AEC firms, so that their teams can make sounder decisions and tackle uncertainties.
        </p>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- CTA Section -->
    <section class="py-20 px-4 bg-blue-600">
      <div class="container mx-auto text-center">
        <h2 class="text-4xl font-bold text-white mb-6">Elevate Your Construction Planning Today</h2>
        <p class="text-xl text-blue-100 mb-8 max-w-2xl mx-auto">
          Join other innovative construction companies who are leveraging ConstructWise's vertical AI to generate better cost estimates and construction schedules.
        </p>
      </div>
    </section>

    <LandingFooter />
  </div>
</BaseLayout>
